<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV23">
<l>vāṉiṟattor cīyamāyva ḷaintavāḷe yiṟṟavaṉ</l>
<l>ūṉiṟattu kirttalama ḻuttiṉāyu lāyacīr</l>
<l>nāṉiṟatta vētanāvar nallayōki ṉālvaṇaṅku</l>
<l>pāṉiṟakka ṭaṟkiṭanta paṟpanāpa ṉallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who, becoming a unique, white-hued lion,</l>
<l>plunged the nails into the fleshy chest of [Hiraṇya] with bright, crooked teeth!</l>
<l>Are You not the Padmanābha who reclined on the milk-hued ocean,</l>
<l>worshipped through yoga by those with the excellent four-fold Vedas of spreading fame</l>
<l rend="indent">on [their] tongues worship?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
